34 WHEREAS, he gave inspiration to many through his high ideals, morals, and deep concern
35 for his fellow citizens, and the devotion, patience, and understanding he demonstrated to his
36 family and friends were admired by others; and
37 WHEREAS, a compassionate and generous man, Steve Mensch will long be remembered for
38 his love of family, friendship, and community and will be missed by all who had the great
39 fortune of knowing him.
40 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
41 the members of this body join in honoring the life and memory of Steve Mensch and express
42 their deepest and most sincere regret at his passing.
43 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
44 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the
45 family of Steve Mensch.
